    <tags>terraform tflint</tags>
    <summary>TFLint is a Terraform linter</summary>
    <description>TFLint is a Terraform linter for detecting errors that can not be detected by terraform plan.

TFLint is a framework and each feature is provided by plugins, the key features are as follows:

- Find possible errors (like invalid instance types) for Major Cloud providers (AWS/Azure/GCP).
- Warn about deprecated syntax, unused declarations.
- Enforce best practices, naming conventions.      
    </description><releaseNotes><![CDATA[### What's Changed

#### Enhancements
* Add support for Terraform v1.15 by @wata727 in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2521
* Bump tflint-ruleset-terraform to v0.15.0 by @wata727 in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2551

#### Chores
* Migrate homebrew-core to third-party tap by @wata727 in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2531
* Revise installation instructions in README.md by @wata727 in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2532
* build(deps): Bump sigstore/cosign-installer from 4.1.1 to 4.1.2 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2535
* build(deps): Bump the go-x group with 3 updates by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2536
* Migrate homebrew auto bump action to GoReleaser by @wata727 in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2534
* Fix variable reference for client-id in release.yml by @wata727 in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2537
* build(deps): Bump golangci/golangci-lint-action from 9.2.0 to 9.2.1 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2546
* build(deps): Bump docker/build-push-action from 7.1.0 to 7.2.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2548
* build(deps): Bump docker/metadata-action from 6.0.0 to 6.1.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2549
* build(deps): Bump docker/login-action from 4.1.0 to 4.2.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2550
* build(deps): Bump the go-x group with 2 updates by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2547
* build(deps): Bump google.golang.org/grpc from 1.81.0 to 1.81.1 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2542
* build(deps): Bump goreleaser/goreleaser-action from 7.2.1 to 7.2.2 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2540
* build(deps): Bump golang from 1.26-alpine3.23 to 1.26.3-alpine3.23 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2541
* build(deps): Bump alpine from 3.23 to 3.23.4 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2539
* Add warning message to installation script by @wata727 in https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/pull/2533

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint/compare/v0.62.1...v0.63.0

]]></releaseNotes>
    
